summary: Test FC device discovery, driver info, PCI host info and rescan functionality
description: |
    This test suite validates FC device capabilities:
    1. Driver Information:
       - Retrieve and verify FC driver information
       - Check driver module details and status
    2. PCI Host Details:
       - Display and validate FC host PCI information
    3. Device Rescan Recovery:
       - Delete FC disk from system
       - Trigger host rescan operation
       - Verify disk reappearance and recovery
       - Validate disk data integrity
component:
    - kernel
test: pytest -v rescan_deleted_disk.py
tier: 1
duration: 2m
